body.name: WADEO 5800W Windproof Camping Stove, Camping Gas Stove with Piezo Ignition and Two Fuel Canister Adapter, Backpacking Stove, Portable Stove for Outdoor Backpacking Hiking and Picnic
deliveryMessages: FREE delivery Wednesday, February 21 on orders shipped by Amazon over $35
features: 【Unique Brass Burner】Compared with stainless material of other brand, the burner of our camping stove is made of brass, consisted of three brass burner, the brass core has a high temperature resistant and anti-corrosion, it is more durable and it will not oxidize black after long time use.

【Strong Power and Windproof Design】With high power of up to 7200W, the backpacking stove heats faster, which helps finish cooking in a short time and improve efficiency. It takes less than 2 minutes to boil 1L water. And the windproof design provides an efficient prevention to wind, which helps improve burning efficiency and save gas fuel.

【Compatible with 3 Kinds of Gas Canister】Our propane camp stove is compatible with isobutane, butane and 1lb propane fuel canister. You can choose the appropriate adapter according to the needs. In addition, the hose of the camping stove is lengthened to 50cm, which is longer than other stove with only 30cm hose. The distance between the stove and the gas cylinder is farther and safer when using.

【Compact and Easy to Carry】The camping stove is only 15.63oz, Light weight and small in size, does not take up much space, easy to carry and store. Great for backpacking, tent camping, and other emergencies. It's a perfect camping stove and an economical choice for camping, trail cooking.
If you encounter problems with the adapter not working, please contact us directly and we will arrange a replacement or a refund
body.description: Butane Adapter We provide a butane adapter - nozzle input and EN417 Lindal valve output, which allows you to change the nozzle bottle to the Lindal valve canister. 1LB Propane Tank Adapter We provide a propane tank adapter is suitable for the 1lb propane small tank to connect the stove, light and any other thing which need EN417 connector, easy to carry when you go out for a picnic.
